#Farntry Isle

## The Island

>[!Important] Farntry Isle is the southern halfe-isle of [[future link here]]. It belongs to the kingdoms of [[missing link]] being divided by the geographic line between the northern forest and the southern desert.

The island of Farntry is connected over land to [[future link here]] via [[Rhein]] and over water to [[Kházdûral Havn]] via [[Berwihl]].

